{"tid":851561,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"屌你老母gym room真係好多死基佬2 （有圖）","createTime":"2018-10-07T08:48:57.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-07T11:20:09.000Z","uid":162644,"like":10,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"ee0c799ade25d669182f16ee42104f65f7ddc72d","tid":851561,"uid":162644,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-07T08:48:57.000Z","msg":"今次又再遇到另一個死基佬真係屌你老母<br />\n頭先做完gym去焗sona,<br />\n由於個sona房好撚細入到去加埋我已經有3個人<br />\n一般桑拿室都有兩排木櫈前面低後面高<br />\n我坐D個位，個基佬最後入黎坐低排C個位<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/07/164852_0759dfab7c781c343b4ac9bb853e348e.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F07%2F164852_0759dfab7c781c343b4ac9bb853e348e.png&h=c14551e7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n之後AB兩個人都走左<br />\n條友就突然黎料，佢右手隻尾指輕輕壓住我左腳腳指尾<br />\n我初頭以為佢唔覺意姐諗住佢會縮關所以無理<br />\n點知佢壓左我4，5秒<br />\n忽然用隻手指尾係到上下掃我隻腳指尾<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我即時爆佢：屌你老母摸乜撚野呀死基佬！<br />\n佢嚇呆左唔識反應我就開門出去<br />\n<br />\n你老母臭系話全世界歧視你班死基佬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n你班死基佬根本唔值得人認同，全部含家產啦去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b558d6ab018a731d097486a94ecbf5efc25da99e","tid":851561,"uid":15691,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-07T08:51:45.000Z","msg":"其實開間專醫基佬既診所會唔會有錢過李+x"},{"pid":"a4bc440e52ca463f3ffc2fc77da0566c82a02f2d","tid":851561,"uid":42188,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-07T08:53:04.000Z","msg":"樓主明明暗爽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"32a9e1e1ee436fbe1fe8e765abba1c5c11fabc12","tid":851561,"uid":143471,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-07T08:53:15.000Z","msg":"點解唔格下劍先走"},{"pid":"88f00ea3b81666757943c3a3fda6ac6435d75884","tid":851561,"uid":162644,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"